# Decky handoff gate

Before marking Deck-facing UI/RPC work complete:

1. Run **`plugin.build`** after `src/`, `main.py`, or `plugin.json` edits.
2. Run preview smoke (`node scripts/run-preview-suite.mjs --tier=smoke`) or **`deck.deploy`** for on-device scenarios.
3. Run **`plugin.diffRpc`** when RPC names changed.
4. For deck-only tags in `tests/preview-suite/deck-only.json`, complete the device QA runbook checklist.
